Preconditions:
- The value of `n` must be greater than or equal to 2.
- The value of `time` must be greater than or equal to 1.

Postconditions:
- The returned index must be between 1 and `n`, inclusive.
- The person holding the pillow after `time` seconds must be the same as the person holding the pillow at the end of the line after `time` seconds.